--- !u!114 &103720647
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 103720643}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: fce8b1ddf3655624590e578fb42cb521, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CompanyInteraction
  questionMark: {fileID: 1602900078}
  companyPanel: {fileID: 2057730542}
  resultPanel: {fileID: 2057730542}
  companyTitleText: {fileID: 1603052537}
  companyBodyText: {fileID: 899156377}
  hintText: {fileID: 877619149}
  resultTitleText: {fileID: 1603052537}
  resultBodyText: {fileID: 899156377}
  resultButtonText: {fileID: 0}
  companyName: <color=#6B4712><size=125%><b>Start Up Company</b></size></color>
  requirementText: '<color=#6B4712><b>Job Description:</b></color>

    Intern role.
    You will be expected to work like a senior, solve problems nobody documented,
    and pretend chaos is "fast-paced learning."


    <color=#6B4712><b>Qualification:</b></color>

    Resume
    score 50+.

    No experience required.

    Willing to survive on vibes.


    <color=#6B4712><b>Offer:</b></color>

    Unpaid.

    You
    will be compensated in "experience," "exposure," and maybe a LinkedIn post.

'
  companyTier: startup
  successResultBody: "<color=#2E7D32><b>APPLICATION RESULT: ACCEPTED</b></color>\nWelcome.
    You have been selected to join this startup. \nOut of thousands of applicants,
    you were the one brave enough to click \u201CApply.\u201D\n\nBefore you begin:\n\u2022
    The position is unpaid.\n\u2022 The compensation is \u201Cexperience.\u201D\n\u2022
    This is non-negotiable.\n\nPlease remember:\nExposure is temporary.\nLinkedIn
    posts are forever.\n\nReport to work immediately. The chaos is already in production."
  requirementBlockedResultBody: "<color=#6B4712><b>Required Before Applying:</b></color>\nYour
    resume is not strong enough for this company yet.\n\nPlease unlock at least one
    of the following:\n\n\u2022 Resume should be above +50 \n\u2022 A GitHub repository
    with commits newer than last semester (optional)\n\u2022 One certification obtained
    after fighting through a 6-hour online course (optional)\n\u2022 Evidence that
    you debugged something at 3AM and survived (A MUST)\n\nReturn after completing
    the side quests."
  declinedResultBody: "<color=#8B0000><b>APPLICATION RESULT: DECLINED</b></color>\nYour
    application has been reviewed by our hiring team.\n\nStep 1: They opened your
    resume.  \nStep 2: Someone said \u201Chmm.\u201D  \nStep 3: The tab was quietly
    closed.\n\nNo hard feelings. This is just our standard startup hiring ritual.\n\n<color=#6B4712><b>Minimum
    Expectations:</b></color>\nYour resume is still not strong enough for this company
    yet.\n\nPlease improve your resume and try again after gaining more \u201Cexperience.\u201D
    Hope to see you again once you return with senior-level skills\u2026 for this
    internship."
