--- !u!114 &350075021
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 350075019}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f37485ae5056c9d43ab6712b77727bd4, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  firstDialogue:
  - Hey buddy Slime, So you just graduated? Bachelor of Science in Software Engineering,
    huh?
  - I had that too. Fresh diploma, big dreams, thought companies would line up the
    moment I updated my resume
  - "Sent out a hundred applications, survived countless interviews, and mastered
    the art of reading \u2018We regret to inform you.\u2019 "
  - "Now I\u2019m debugging my life on this sidewalk. "
  - "Still excited to start your job hunt? So if the offers never come\u2026 there\u2019s
    always a spot next to me out here. Rent\u2019s free. "
  secondDialogue:
  - "Back again? Did you land a job yet? I\u2019m still holding your spot in the
    neighborhood, just in case."
  dialoguePanel: {fileID: 1993142769}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 712370669}
  autoLineDuration: 2.5
